scene_description_enriched: A man, appearing ill or wounded with a beard and long hair, sits draped in a white cloth. He points to his chest. Two other men stand behind him, one in a yellow and brown striped robe, the other in a blue robe and hat, holding a lute. The man in the blue robe gestures with his hand. In the background, a stylized grey building with arched windows is visible. The scene is set against a blue sky and appears to be outdoors.
